{%- comment -%}
  Ganguram — read-only "Delivering to: <zone> <pincode>" cart line (Phase 2.10A).

  Subtle, display-only. Rendered at the top of the cart (drawer + page); starts
  hidden and is populated client-side by ganguram-cart-attributes.js from the
  SELECTED pincode/zone (window.GanguramZone). No cart / checkout / eligibility /
  removal logic lives here — it is purely informational.
{%- endcomment -%}
<div class="ganguram-cart-delivery-summary" data-ganguram-cart-delivery-summary hidden>
  <span class="ganguram-cart-delivery-summary__label" data-gcd-label></span>
  <span class="ganguram-cart-delivery-summary__value" data-gcd-value></span>
</div>
